PAID

            PAID System


            Security changes were recently made to PAID. In order to access the
            system you must use browser with 128-bit encryption.

            If you would prefer to receive your payment information in the email
            itself, please change your service to "Email Data Delivery" and you
            will no longer need to log into the system to view your information.

